Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.61,0:00:13.45,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Killer Queen! This is the name I've chosen for it.{copied from 21}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.66,0:00:17.08,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I'm going to completely eliminate you...{copied from 21}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.08,0:00:19.91,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,...so that my sleep will go undisturbed tonight.{copied from 21}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.91,0:00:23.67,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,I toldja nots t'move!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.67,0:00:25.92,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Don't takes my Harvest lightly!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.17,0:00:28.29,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Die! {I added this, not sure if it's a Stand battle cry that I never knew Kira had, in which case it should stay like this, or if it's a word that CR left without a line for some reason.}{Xemnas: Xemnas has no idea either way}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.71,0:00:32.34,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,You have this many?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.34,0:00:35.97,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Crushing just three or four of them \Nhardly seems to damage you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.84,0:00:42.10,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,If ya moves even a lil', \NI'll cut yer whatchamacallit artery or whatevers!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.10,0:00:45.19,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Oh yeah! It's da carotid artery!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.19,0:00:49.23,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,I swear I'll cuts it!\N Dere ain't nobody dat can beats my Harvest!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.23,0:00:56.16,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Looks t'me like ya gots a power-type Stand dat can't go very far!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.16,0:00:59.49,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,It only gots a one or two meter range, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.49,0:01:03.20,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,, If ya wants t'die, den jus' try'n move!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.12,0:01:10.50,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I see... So each individual user has a unique power?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.80,0:01:15.01,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,A Stand? Hmm... Stands, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.43,0:01:21.47,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,By the way, my Killer Queen \Npossesses a special power of its own...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.89,0:01:25.77,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,He gots somethin'... Geddit!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.81,0:01:30.69,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Huh? Dis's jus' a 100 yen coin...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.69,0:01:32.73,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,What're ya doin' with dis?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.73,0:01:38.28,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Nothing much.\N I just wanted to show you my Killer Queen's special power...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.28,0:01:42.74,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,...seeing as how you're as good as dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.74,0:01:45.62,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Killer Queen's special power...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.62,0:01:50.34,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,...is that it can turn anything it touches into a bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.21,0:01:53.34,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Literally anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.09,0:01:56.72,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,For example, a 100 yen coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.22,0:02:00.97,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Get rid of dat 100 yen coin, Harvest!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.02,0:02:16.19,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,With that out of the way, I can finally rest well tonight.
Comment: 0,0:02:16.99,0:02:17.03,Main,,0,0,0,,OPENING
Comment: 0,0:03:30.48,0:03:30.52,Main,,0,0,0,,B
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.81,0:03:35.40,Title Part 4,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(648,643)\pos(143,890)\fs60}Episode 22: {\fs80} Kira Yoshikage Wants a Quiet Life Part 2
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.98,0:03:37.15,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,{\an8}Did you hear about that salon that helps you find your true love?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:39.90,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,{\an8}Huh? Seriously? That's so dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.90,0:03:42.49,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's true! One of the high school girls did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:45.87,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,It seems one blast wasn't enough to finish the job...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.99,0:03:51.41,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Wh-What's goin' on? What...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.41,0:03:52.50,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,What da...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:04:00.01,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,What happened t'me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:01.59,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I already told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:05.97,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,My Killer Queen can turn anything it touches into a bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.97,0:04:09.18,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I turned this 100 yen coin into a bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.18,0:04:15.90,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I can trigger the switch whenever I want,\N blowing my opponent to bits from the inside out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.27,0:04:18.11,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Though in your case, Shigechi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.11,0:04:21.40,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,...half of your face blew into your head...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.40,0:04:27.41,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,...and about a third of your brain \Ngot mixed in with the flesh of your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.91,0:04:34.21,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Before I finish you off with this next blow, \Nthere's something I would like to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.21,0:04:36.58,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,These abilities you call Stands...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:40.92,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Do your friends, Josuke and Okuyasu, also have them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.92,0:04:43.42,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,S-Somebody help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:46.72,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Oh, no, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.72,0:04:49.10,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,You won't be leaving here alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:52.06,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I can't leave any living witnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:58.19,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,No one can know the true identity of I, Kira Yoshikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:05:02.99,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,However, I'm interested in knowing of other Stand users.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:08.07,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I can easily investigate who they are myself, \Nbut I figured it wouldn't hurt to ask you first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:10.58,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Josuke, Okuyasu...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.08,0:05:13.04,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Can you give me any other names?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:16.58,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,How many more of them live in this town?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:18.83,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,What powers do they have?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.83,0:05:21.67,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,I-I dunno...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:24.42,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Don't tell me that you don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.42,0:05:27.30,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Listen, if you aren't willing to tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.76,0:05:30.43,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,...I'll have to eliminate your parents, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:32.10,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.97,0:05:35.14,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,...What'd ya say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.14,0:05:38.15,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,M-My Papa and Mama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.15,0:05:39.94,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Hurry up and tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.94,0:05:42.48,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,If you do, nothing will happen to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:46.03,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,We may be discovered if you take too long to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.32,0:05:49.74,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Just give me their names. Come on, make it quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.74,0:05:55.79,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,E-Everyone was lookin' fer a serial killer here in town!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.37,0:06:00.17,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,A serial killer... Dey was talkin' 'bout you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.17,0:06:03.55,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Yer da one who killed Sugimoto Reimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:05.84,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,What? Sugimoto Reimi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:10.72,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,He can still use his Stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:12.51,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Killer Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.02,0:06:20.81,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,That brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.81,0:06:23.44,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,He was so torn up, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.03,0:06:37.46,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,I... I gots t'find... Josuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:42.63,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Josuke's Crazy Diamond...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.96,0:06:48.38,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,...can heals me up...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.30,0:06:56.68,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,I... I gots t'save Papa an' Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:07:02.23,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,I gots t'save Papa an' Mama from dat bad man!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.31,0:07:06.98,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Dat no good, nasty man...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:12.70,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,...can't be livin' in da same town with Papa an' Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:21.58,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,I gots t'find him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:26.46,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,I gots t'find Mr. Josuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:30.38,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.38,0:07:32.84,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,Hey, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.34,0:07:35.97,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,I gots t'find him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.97,0:07:38.14,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,He looks hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:40.35,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,Is he from the middle school?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.48,0:07:44.69,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,Th-There's something wrong with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.69,0:07:46.52,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,We should get a teacher...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.52,0:07:48.94,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,No, leave him alone. He's creepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:50.99,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,Let's go...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.33,0:07:59.20,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,J-Josuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:06.46,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,J-Josuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.30,0:08:17.47,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,You said everyone was looking for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.47,0:08:22.85,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Do you mean to tell me someone in this town \Nknows the nature of Sugimoto Reimi's death?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.81,0:08:27.52,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I can't allow anyone to pursue me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.23,0:08:32.57,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,No one else knows the identity of I, Kira Yoshikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.57,0:08:36.12,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Which is why I need you gone for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:41.12,Thoughts,Shigechi,0,0,0,,I gots t'keep my Papa an' Mama safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.66,0:08:47.00,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Killer Queen already touched that doorknob.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.13,0:08:55.18,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Josuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.39,0:09:03.52,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,This is the power of Killer Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:07.81,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,He's been eliminated without a trace.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.19,0:09:10.94,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Was someone just calling my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.94,0:09:12.69,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Yeah, I heard it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.69,0:09:15.61,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Whoa! H-Hey, Josuke, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.16,0:09:26.08,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Got... cha!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:28.83,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Sh-Shigechi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.80,0:09:32.25,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Shigechi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:35.84,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Th-This ain't good, Josuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.84,0:09:38.43,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Harvest was gushin' blood after it disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.43,0:09:40.85,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,That ain't how Stands're supposed to disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.85,0:09:44.60,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Why do ya think one of those \NHarvest dudes showed up right in fronta us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.11,0:09:52.15,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Let's go to the middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:53.86,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,We have to find Shigechi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.15,0:10:01.08,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Damn... When did that fall off?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.08,0:10:03.12,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Well, it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.62,0:10:07.75,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Hopefully my usual tailor has the same button.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.06,0:10:25.31,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,How awful...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.56,0:10:30.10,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,He struck again... It was him...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.94,0:10:34.90,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,The soul of another one of his victims is flying away...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.69,0:10:38.90,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,That boy must have run into him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.58,0:10:46.87,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Shigechi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.18,0:11:02.85,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.85,0:11:04.51,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,This boy is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.31,0:11:09.89,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,Poor Shigekiyo ran into him, then was murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.89,0:11:11.44,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,I'm certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.19,0:11:17.94,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,I don't know under what circumstances \Nthe two of them met or how he killed that boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.32,0:11:20.20,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,...but I'm sure it was him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.86,0:11:24.33,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,I know it was him since he killed me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:29.12,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I looked for Shigechi everywhere, but I couldn't find him...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.12,0:11:33.42,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,He disappeared less than five minutes \Nafter Okuyasu and I left.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.34,0:11:39.92,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,All of Shigechi's books and school supplies were left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:42.72,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,His parents have the police searching for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.64,0:11:44.68,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,This probably means...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.68,0:11:48.89,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,D-Do you mean... the killer is a Stand user?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:54.48,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I know most of you probably don't know much about Shigechi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.48,0:11:58.69,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,...but it's hard for me to imagine anyone \Nwho could beat Harvest in a direct confrontation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.69,0:12:04.32,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,This guy killed Shigechi in less than five minutes, \Nthen somehow hid his body somewhere inside the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.82,0:12:09.79,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Jotaro, since we're almost certainly \Ndealing with a Stand user here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.79,0:12:12.54,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,...we have no choice but to lend our assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:13.92,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Josuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.33,0:12:16.04,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I heard you picked up a button.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:19.92,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Yeah... Harvest brought it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.30,0:12:21.30,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.01,0:12:25.43,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,This is Shigechi's final message.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.43,0:12:30.43,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,It's possible Harvest may have ripped it \Nfrom the serial killer's clothes just to bring it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.43,0:12:33.85,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I'm gonna hold on to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.85,0:12:35.02,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I need to investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.02,0:12:39.32,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Y-You can find that guy using a button \N that could have come from anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.32,0:12:40.53,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Possibly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.86,0:12:44.61,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,We may be able to figure out the brand of clothing\N he was wearing and where it came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.61,0:12:46.41,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.41,0:12:50.87,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,I-If we're done here, I'm gonna go home...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.16,0:12:54.79,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,I-I ain't feelin' so good...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.79,0:12:56.79,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,I-I'm gettin' all pissed off...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.46,0:12:59.34,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Let's go home, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.88,0:13:03.51,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,There's something wrong with Okuyasu...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.51,0:13:08.80,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Yeah... Shigechi was a greedy, annoying little jerk...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.80,0:13:12.06,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,...but he was the type of guy you just couldn't help but like.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.06,0:13:14.98,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,It's hard to believe that he's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.39,0:13:24.03,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I'm not totally sure, but I think Okuyasu is upset since he doesn't know whether to feel sad or angry right now... {changed pissed to upset since pissed = angry. I didn't really like saying "he's angry because he doesnt know if he should be sad or angry", I think "upset" is more general that can mean sad or angry and might fit better.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.03,0:13:26.11,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I'm going through the same thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.11,0:13:29.28,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,...but it's probably even worse for Okuyasu...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.28,0:13:30.78,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Fuck...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:34.79,Main,Yukako,0,0,0,,It seems terrible things were happening that I didn't notice...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.79,0:13:38.83,Main,Tonio,0,0,0,,I must be warning each of my customers who dine at my restaurant of this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.83,0:13:43.55,Main,Aya,0,0,0,,I don't believe he'll come to my place, but just in case...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.55,0:13:47.51,Main,Hazamada,0,0,0,,Even though Stand users are drawn to other Stand users...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:50.18,Main,Hazamada,0,0,0,,...I never wanna meet that asshole.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.22,0:13:54.56,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,So everyone here plans to take action, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.63,0:14:20.33,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:23.46,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,That was Josuke just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.30,0:14:27.05,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Okuyasu was with him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.76,0:14:30.22,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,Hey, get a load of this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.22,0:14:33.31,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,Last Friday was my birthday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.31,0:14:38.98,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,That guy I've been going out with \Ngave me this stupid ring as a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.98,0:14:41.65,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,Look at this thing! Why would I want this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.65,0:14:45.82,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,I still did the whole "I love it so much!" thing for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.82,0:14:49.95,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,I'm only dating him since his dad is super rich, because otherwise he's a complete loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.95,0:14:54.08,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,This ring is so gaudy! How much was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:56.20,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,Probably around 150,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:14:58.62,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,I can just pawn it off for some money.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.62,0:15:02.21,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be caught dead with this thing on my finger!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.79,0:15:06.09,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,That woman has an ugly heart, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.09,0:15:09.30,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,...her hands and face are so soft and beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:13.72,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,By dating me, her soul will be cleansed of its filth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:16.35,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,I have to go now. See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.35,0:15:18.10,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,Okay, bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.94,0:15:25.19,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I'm afraid that's it for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.19,0:15:27.44,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I'm glad it was a clean farewell.
Comment: 0,0:15:37.95,0:15:38.00,Main,,0,0,0,,C
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.42,0:15:53.97,Narrator,Kai,0,0,0,,{\an8}Greetings, all. It's Morioh Radio!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.97,0:15:57.31,Narrator,Kai,0,0,0,,{\an8}Coming at you once again is yours truly, Kai Harada.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.31,0:16:01.10,Narrator,Kai,0,0,0,,{\an8}How has the beginning of the week been treating you all so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.10,0:16:03.81,Narrator,Kai,0,0,0,,{\an8}There's just a few short days left in June now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.81,0:16:08.23,Narrator,Kai,0,0,0,,{\an8}And come July... That's right, it's vacation time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.23,0:16:11.40,Narrator,Kai,0,0,0,,{\an8}What kind of plans do you lovely listeners have?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.40,0:16:13.49,Narrator,Kai,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.49,0:16:20.08,Narrator,Kai,0,0,0,,{\an8}Coming up, the perfect song for this sunny day happening in the middle of the rainy season!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.08,0:16:22.00,Narrator,Kai,0,0,0,,{\an8}Please, enjoy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:04.86,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Now, let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.98,0:16:07.61,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.61,0:16:12.57,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I have some errands to run today, \Nso I would like you to stay home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.49,0:16:17.74,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,We'll eat dinner together when I get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.37,0:16:26.13,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,I'm so happy they still had the Parisian Special!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:28.88,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,You're so lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.34,0:16:28.88,Secondary,Girl,0,0,0,,Let's hurry to Yohee Station!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.88,0:16:30.26,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,Wait, Asuka isn't here yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.26,0:16:33.47,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,{\an8}Really? What's taking her so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.13,0:16:35.26,Thoughts,Koichi,0,0,0,,It's been four days since the incident with Shigechi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.93,0:16:41.06,Thoughts,Koichi,0,0,0,,Nothing much has happened since then, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.56,0:16:48.02,Thoughts,Koichi,0,0,0,,...now we have undeniable proof that \Na serial killer is still running rampant in our town.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.57,0:16:52.28,Thoughts,Koichi,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth, \Nwhen I look at the faces of people passing by...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:55.91,Thoughts,Koichi,0,0,0,,...I can't even tell if they look innocent or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.50,0:17:07.83,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Oh! H-How are you doing, Mr. Jotaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.13,0:17:12.46,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Umm, have you learned anything new since I last saw you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:16.72,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,You know, like about the serial killer's button or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:19.47,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:21.14,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Don't have any leads yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.72,0:17:23.89,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.86,0:17:31.86,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Umm, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.44,0:17:36.36,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Nowhere, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.36,0:17:37.86,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Just over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:39.32,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.33,0:17:43.95,Thoughts,Koichi,0,0,0,,This is rough...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.95,0:17:46.75,Thoughts,Koichi,0,0,0,,It's hard to hold up a conversation with him \Nwhen he hardly talks...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.75,0:17:52.42,Thoughts,Koichi,0,0,0,,Unlike Mr. Rohan's overbearing personality,\N it's Jotaro's silent demeanor that makes him scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.42,0:17:56.51,Thoughts,Koichi,0,0,0,,What can I talk to him about? Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:17:59.26,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,That's a nice coat you're wearing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.22,0:18:04.56,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Looks like this is a shoe store. {No fucking shit}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.56,0:18:08.52,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, yeah, it is a shoe store.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.52,0:18:10.02,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.27,0:18:20.41,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Even though it's just a shoe store, they do some simple stuff, too,\N like adjusting the waist measurements on skirts, and hemming pants.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:22.91,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,There's even an electronics shop around here that sells flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.91,0:18:25.16,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Is that what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.16,0:18:28.37,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I checked out all of the tailors around Morioh, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.37,0:18:31.54,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,...I didn't bother looking into places like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.80,0:18:41.18,Main,Old Dude,0,0,0,,You having a problem with this button?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.18,0:18:44.93,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,No. If you've never seen it before, then don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.93,0:18:48.73,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I just forgot what it was originally attached to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.19,0:18:53.19,Main,Old Dude,0,0,0,,Kid, you want an animal cracker?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.69,0:18:59.32,Main,Old Dude,0,0,0,,I like eating the camel last, \Nso pick any of the others that you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.32,0:19:01.16,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,No thanks, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.16,0:19:02.95,Main,Old Dude,0,0,0,,Oh, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:06.20,Main,Old Dude,0,0,0,,Anyway, not only have I seen that button before...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.20,0:19:11.29,Main,Old Dude,0,0,0,,...I actually just got finished repairing the suit it came off of.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.29,0:19:16.46,Main,Old Dude,0,0,0,,A customer came in yesterday\N asking me for this exact same button.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.38,0:19:19.97,Main,Old Dude,0,0,0,,See? It's the same button.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.97,0:19:21.26,Main,Koi,0,0,0,,Mr. Jotaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.26,0:19:24.22,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Gimme a break. We actually found it, Koichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:25.35,Main,Old Dude,0,0,0,,Found it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.35,0:19:27.10,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Oh, n-nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.10,0:19:29.68,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,B-But more importantly, what did the customer look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.68,0:19:31.23,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Do you know his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.23,0:19:32.52,Main,Old Dude,0,0,0,,His name?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.52,0:19:36.02,Main,Old Dude,0,0,0,,Of course I know his name. \NDo you take me for a fool?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.02,0:19:40.03,Main,Old Dude,0,0,0,,I haven't forgotten the name of a single one of my customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.03,0:19:46.45,Main,Old Dude,0,0,0,,That's just common courtesy when you deal with \Nthe same customers, even if you have hundreds or thousands!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:47.45,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.08,0:19:52.37,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Yes! That's amazing! \NCan you tell us his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.42,0:19:59.46,Main,Old Dude,0,0,0,,Well, the jacket should have an order tag attached to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.97,0:20:03.97,Main,Old Dude,0,0,0,,I mean, I remember his name, \Neven though I've had hundreds of customers...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.34,0:20:07.47,Main,Old Dude,0,0,0,,...but it will be faster to just look at the tag.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:14.15,Main,Old Dude,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.65,0:20:17.94,Main,Old Dude,0,0,0,,His surname is... How do you read this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.53,0:20:19.94,Main,Old Dude,0,0,0,,I think it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.94,0:20:23.20,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Wh-What is it? C-Can you show me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.61,0:20:27.20,Main,Old Dude,0,0,0,,Umm... Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.26,0:20:45.64,Main,SHA,0,0,0,,Look over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.80,0:20:50.22,Main,Old Dude,0,0,0,,Wh-What the hell?! My hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:52.60,Main,SHA,0,0,0,,Look over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.60,0:20:55.06,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,M-Mr. Jotaro! L-Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.06,0:20:57.86,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Be careful, Koichi! Don't get any closer to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.15,0:21:02.36,Main,SHA,0,0,0,,Hey, I told you to look over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.16,0:21:15.46,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Is that his Stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.21,0:21:20.55,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,M-Mr. Jotaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.34,0:21:25.38,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,H-He's here! He's trying to take the jacket!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.68,0:21:34.48,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I didn't suspect anyone would actually investigate the button that fell off my jacket...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.48,0:21:37.94,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Did they see my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.56,0:21:41.94,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Why have these things been happening to me lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.94,0:21:43.44,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Gimme a break...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.44,0:21:45.86,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I can't believe he chose {\i1}now{\i0} to pick up his suit...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.57,0:21:52.41,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Regardless, I will make them disappear... using my Killer Queen's Secondary Bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.41,0:21:55.29,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Just like that brat, Shigechi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.92,0:21:58.58,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,It's still moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.25,0:22:00.88,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,That jacket is important evidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.88,0:22:01.88,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.30,0:22:04.34,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Don't make any hasty decisions without thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.34,0:22:07.84,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,The way he's tugging on it is suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.35,0:22:17.73,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Something about this Stand...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.36,0:22:22.98,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,...seems really dangerous!
