Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.63,0:02:38.80,Part 4 OP2 English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\1c&HFAF2ED&}Something important is being taken from me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.80,0:02:41.22,Part 4 OP2 English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\1c&HFAF2ED&}By a demon that's thrust itself into my life
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.22,0:02:44.60,Part 4 OP2 English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\1c&HC4B3D4&}Everything is crumbling around me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.22,0:02:47.39,Part 4 OP2 English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\1c&HECEEEE&}Living my life as if everything was fine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.39,0:02:49.77,Part 4 OP2 English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\1c&HECEEEE&}Until suddenly it was stolen away without warning
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.77,0:02:53.23,Part 4 OP2 English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\1c&HECEEEE&}This is my only chance to take it back
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.23,0:02:57.57,Part 4 OP2 English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\1c&HF8E3D2&}Those who fight with a heart pierced by the arrow
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.57,0:03:01.07,Part 4 OP2 English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\1c&HF8E3D2&}Are a beautiful sight to behold
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.07,0:03:02.12,Part 4 OP2 English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)}{\1c&HF8E3D2&}Anywhere you go I'll chase you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.12,0:03:03.74,Part 4 OP2 English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)}{\1c&HC3F0FA&}Anywhere you go I'll chase you
