Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.87,0:03:08.04,Part 4 OP2 English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\1c&HC3F0FA&}I will chase you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.04,0:03:09.62,Part 4 OP2 English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\1c&HD6ECF9&}You can't escape me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:12.29,Part 4 OP2 English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\1c&HD6ECF9&}Run faster as I chase you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.29,0:03:14.42,Part 4 OP2 English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\1c&HD6ECF9&}Even tomorrow I'll chase you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:17.30,Part 4 OP2 English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\1c&HD6ECF9&}Until I finally pummel you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.30,0:03:22.93,Part 4 OP2 English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\1c&&HEEF7F1&&}My perseverance will propel me forward to achieve victory
